<bibRefCitation author="Queiroz, L. P. &amp; Snak, C." box="[1011,1321,475,502]" pageId="13" pageNumber="30" pagination="67 - 114" refId="ref18123" refString="Queiroz, L. P. &amp; Snak, C. (2020) Revisiting the taxonomy of Dioclea and related genera (Leguminosae, Papilionoideae), with new generic circumscriptions. PhytoKeys 164: 67 - 114. https: // doi. org / 10.3897 / phytokeys. 164.55441" type="journal article" year="2020">Queiroz &amp; Snak (2020: 96)</bibRefCitation>
